                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - S
                   ====================================

                                Steel Eagle
                                ===========



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(32895,0)"}          32895,0
@{"No Recharge   " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(35572,0) zxampoke(35563,0)"}          35563,0:35575,0



                         This POKE works for both 48K and 128K versions.

                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
